            . I went to the Pultney Hotel, and found the prisoner there; I found these handkerchiefs between the bed and the sacking. The prisoner said at first, they were given to him.</p>
               <p>MRS. WRIGHT re-examined. The handkerchiefs produced were her property. I never heard the prisoner complain against my servant for taking any part of his property.</p>
